trans-unit.source: Provides a simple implementation of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Gir en enkel implementering av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer"> </xref> grensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceContainer object can be used to store and provide services.
trans-unit.target: ServiceContainer-objektet kan brukes til å lagre og tjenester.

trans-unit.source: ServiceContainer implements the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> interface.
trans-unit.target: ServiceContainer implementerer den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>grensesnittet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>

trans-unit.source: The ServiceContainer object can be created using a constructor that adds a parent <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> through which services can be optionally added to or removed from all parent <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> objects, including the immediate parent <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>.
trans-unit.target: ServiceContainer kan opprette objektet ved hjelp av en konstruktør som legger til en overordnet <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>som services kan eventuelt legges til eller fjernet fra alle overordnede <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>objekter, inkludert umiddelbare overordnede <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>

trans-unit.source: To add or remove a service from all <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> implementations that are linked to this <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> through parenting, call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.AddService%2A> or <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.RemoveService%2A> method overload that accepts a Boolean value indicating whether to promote the service request.
trans-unit.target: Legge til eller fjerne en tjeneste fra alle <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>implementeringer som er koblet til denne <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>via overordning, kan du kalle den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.AddService%2A>eller <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.RemoveService%2A>overlasten for metoden som godtar en boolsk verdi som angir om å fremme serviceforespørselen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.RemoveService%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.AddService%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IServiceContainer>

trans-unit.source: Disposes this service container.
trans-unit.target: Disposes denne beholderen.

trans-unit.source: Dispose walks all instantiated services within the container and disposes any that implement <xref:System.IDisposable>, and clears the service list.
trans-unit.target: Avhending går gjennom alle forekomstopprettet tjenester i beholderen og disposes alle som Implementer <xref:System.IDisposable>, og fjerner tjeneste-listen.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A> when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>.
trans-unit.target: Kall <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>Når du er ferdig med <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A> method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>metoden forlater den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>ble bruker.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A> before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Ring alltid <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>

trans-unit.source: Disposes this service container.
trans-unit.target: Disposes denne beholderen.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A> walks all instantiated services within the container and disposes any that implement <xref:System.IDisposable>, and clears the service list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>går gjennom alle forekomstopprettet tjenester i beholderen og disposes alle som Implementer <xref:System.IDisposable>, og fjerner tjeneste-listen.</xref:System.IDisposable></xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()`method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()`metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>referanser.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ServiceContainer>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.
